    "longBusinessSummary": "Central Hydropower Joint Stock Company produces, transmits, and distributes electricity in Vietnam. The company engages in construction of solar and wind power plants; consulting on construction of electrical projects, solar power plant, and wind energy power plant; production of metal structures; consulting and designing power grids and systems; exploitation and trading of construction materials; aquaculture; investment, construction, housing business and rental, tourist accommodation business; restaurant business; construction of traffic works; domestic and international travel service business; entertainment area business; dredging the lake bed; construction of civil engineering works and houses for living; testing service; vocational training; and exploitation of wood from planted forests. It is also involved in manufacturing of measuring, testing, navigation and control equipment; repair of machinery and equipment; repair of electrical equipment; installation of machinery and industrial equipment, electrical systems, water supply, drainage, heating, and air conditioning systems; manufacturing electrical equipment and electrical accessories; and manufacturing mechanical equipment. Central Hydropower Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Da Nang, Vietnam.",
